flowchart TD
    Start([Início]) --> Basics[basics · universal]
    Basics --> Q1{Q1 · injury_phase}
    Q1 -->|acute| BranchA[🔴 Branch: Aguda]
    Q1 -->|subacute| Default[Fluxo padrão]
    Q1 -->|chronic| BranchC[🟠 Branch: Crônica]
    Q1 -->|returning| BranchR[🟢 Branch: Retornando]
    BranchA --> Q2
    Default --> Q2
    BranchC --> Q2
    BranchR --> Q2
    Q2[Q2 · injury_location] --> Q3[Q3 · current_capacity]
    Q3 -->|cannot_walk| Safety1[🚨 safetyReduced]
    Q3 -->|walk_only / run_*| Q4
    Safety1 --> Q4
    Q4[Q4 · return_blocker] --> Q5[Q5 · injury_history]
    Q5 --> Q6[Q6 · pre_injury_volume]
    Q6 --> Q7{Q7 · health_conditions}
    Q7 -->|stress_fracture / progressive / numbness / cardiac| Safety2[🚨 safetyReduced]
    Q7 -->|safe| PN
    Safety2 --> PN
    PN[personal_note · universal] --> Goal[goal · universal] --> Contact[contact · universal] --> End([relatório IA])

    classDef decision fill:#fff3e0,stroke:#f57c00
